Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收手吧 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意欲何为 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道兄长你的性欲乃大陆首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然放着碗里的妹妹不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将魔手伸向嘉依卡 实在是不能睡视不理呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽点太多我都不知从哪吐起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我声明我是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您太谦虚了 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无防备睡在一旁的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对兄长你来说 不就如同摆在猛兽眼前的生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我当成什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奇伊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还记得啊 值得夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何贵干? 又带来了什么新情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了下一位英雄的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亚 科尼柯赛克王国的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后确认其行踪是在四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这三日车程的 拉德米欧市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少能当作个追寻他的线索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实打从一开始就全都知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 至少我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过是一名使者罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得是上了你的套 令人很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 那挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情地怀疑 苦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正希望你们如此

Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不归谷

Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走过路过不要错过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有南方矿山挖出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高纯度的魔法思念料喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 品种齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个要 这个也买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不归谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是个经常布满浓雾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可自从四年前起 一点也不放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入谷者没人再出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出了弃兽啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟就连去确认的人们 也都没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知都还是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失踪? 西蒙·斯坎尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这男人原来是军中的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但战争结束后 马上就失去了踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没想到被称作英雄的男人竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些日子的阿巴尔特伯爵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认已经病死的多明妮卡·斯考达也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为辉煌的八英雄的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不免感到诧异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还有传闻 说这是贾兹皇帝的诅咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么活了五百年 能使用怪物般的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟那是个有着各种诡异传说的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻先不说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但贾兹皇帝的遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是从金钱的角度 或是作为高纯度的魔法思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是无以伦比的绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此说不定得到它 会导致人们丧失正常的判断力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若嘉依卡一行人打算接触西蒙·斯坎尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该会在这拉德米欧市现身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会继续调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正驭使小枭进行探查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想确认下 他有没有在聚精会神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也别用针刺他头来试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「针」对你来说 就如同对我来说的「剑」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不应该轻易拔出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器能救人 也能伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重选择使用之处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到那队嘉依卡·贾兹及乱破师了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在城市另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亚 住所不归谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正好和他消失的时期相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 准备机杖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持随时能发动的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 离这么远也能感知到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面应该还有魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做无益的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白日做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·贾兹 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收集贾兹皇帝的遗体 到底有什么企图?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭悼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说 你的目的就仅仅如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能轻信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是她为了逃走而随口编的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 嘉依卡能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去做掉基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没什么胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战意已决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就全力以赴 一决雌雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士 亚伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此对汝等宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是厮杀?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁真不公平!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我一份啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她们同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我情愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跑呢 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶~? 那厮杀呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想我死在其他人之手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装铠龙居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 再晚一点就危险了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 全部遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再买不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢? 回机车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那帮家伙还在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不方便接近城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往北边飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越过森林应该有个浓雾山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显现吧 探测者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测魔法 无效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…那也是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法? 那雾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理论上 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 庞大力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力源 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性 有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不能贸然下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想从空中观察一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能载着我们 去山谷上方转一圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为托鲁你言而无信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是 明明说好帮你就和我打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没说不和你打啊 总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天是几时?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天? 明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天就是总有一天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 不管管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体 这下面 探索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样应该没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我还能怎么办!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做了那个时候的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到现在我仍偶尔会想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时从悬崖上摔下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许活下来的不该是我 而是阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 不要责备自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆因有托鲁一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我世上最重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说也是 若我没遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也过不上这样充实的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因有你在我身边 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然应尽早处理掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 请求 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情 不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可能性 魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影 精神支配 多重效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁的妄想 成形显现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等我啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神影响 雾所变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘉依卡 以及建筑 全都是雾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…既然会见到那种幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说兄长心中有那样的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下流无耻 必须立即唤醒兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除结界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守护者」魔法效果范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除 立即 与雾接触
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到精神支配 与托鲁同样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是不能吸到雾?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能在这眼睁睁看着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法 只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.16,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 到这边来 良机到来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法解除 托鲁捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法再度 起动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这旅途也接近尾声了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只剩下一件遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打败亚伯力克·基烈特抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有困难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不用再收集遗体了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来接你了 嘉依卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伯力克!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伯力克?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要与亚伯力克结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈? 结婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 那收集遗体呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要和亚伯力克在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的遗体自然就能到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我好高兴!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我祭悼完父亲 我们就举办婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可你不是说要和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为一国的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然是要挑选个门当户对的对象才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可能一直和个低贱乱破师混在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 至今多谢你啦托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会无期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此别过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 请等等 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要抛弃我吗~~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除结界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要丢下我独自一人~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.11,0:15:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦啦 醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来一切都是幻觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔下来时 只有托鲁没能回收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下来该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到结界外 就又幻觉丛生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无法移动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干涉魔法 雾中击入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方魔法 部分妨害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击入魔法的那一部分 就可以自由行走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法发动 移动 反复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 然后再破坏掉对方的机杖就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过啊 那个魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是出于什么目的才施加了这种魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到本人直接问他就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若他还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统率者 显现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统率者 显现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eim Halmus Rom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naint milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来魔法解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亚在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没礼貌 擅自闯入别人家中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西蒙·斯坎尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏掉了 真是不中用的废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.69,0:18:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底魔法这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键时刻就连个屁用都顶不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是西蒙·斯坎尼亚吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙? 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什么西蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得八英雄中有这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再回军队 绝不回…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部队位置被敌人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差点就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点就死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我之外 大家全死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马鲁克那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙把部队出卖给了敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那混蛋 还摆出一副好友的嘴脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是马鲁克的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 马鲁克那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是在讲战争时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还把艾蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的至爱妻子夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个那个都是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到了同伴和妻子的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是离开军队 独自住在了这样的山谷里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 刚才的魔法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪被骗的人自己傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣 绝望 然后全都化为白骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是想让人看到被信任之人背叛的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让别人也遭受和他同样的经历吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我刚才那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体 返还 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 女儿 贾兹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贾兹 女儿…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲祭悼 遗体 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗体?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那正可谓这世上最无用的破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要就赶紧拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么? 舍不得?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 那种东西我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 若要回拉德米欧市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能爬上这崖壁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明被称作英雄 还得到了财产和遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下场却这么悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.24,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我想那么多也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁 善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这倒不是因为善良…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻觉 我与托鲁两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个嘛 别太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 背叛 不会 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲起来 那怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎会和嘉依卡那样…对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过毕竟阿卡莉和芙蕾多妮卡是绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也许只好选了嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长 为什么我是绝对不可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 想想就知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…你好像生气了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶中!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.36,0:23:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山岭的帝国?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朴实的人们 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 大家 故乡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我 祖国记忆 基本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第八集 「暂慰的帝国」

