Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,// OPEDC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:06.69,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:11.37,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:29.87,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天这样的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.52,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:40.49,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏过所有的困难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.51,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:49.43,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}恋爱笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:53.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手无策 在这深夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投无路 遵守着约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:03.20,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己镜中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我们不要被条框锁住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:14.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼凑的时光又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:21.05,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告别 这种答案毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:26.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只会继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:23.72,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行尸走肉般走过的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:29.23,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}头顶的阳光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.44,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何时你已经沦落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:40.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}连自己名字也都遗忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.36,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人类 为何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.03,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.94,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}这无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:56.65,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如随之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.64,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}无常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:09.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}从寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 听风带来山林的回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}请看 指引我们的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:19.91,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}就是斩断悲哀的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:24.52,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}别害怕 别颤抖 活下去

Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,// OPEDJ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:06.69,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}がんじがらめの自由なんて僕たちはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:11.37,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}つぎはぎだらけな中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:29.87,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}今日みたいな日があるから　生きていけるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.52,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}って思う　って思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:40.49,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}君って人がいるから　越えていけるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:44.51,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}って思う　って思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:49.43,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}愛の馬鹿　視界不良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:53.61,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}どうしろって言うんだ　この夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.61,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行き止まり　で指切り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:03.20,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}自分の鏡に　映し出せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.04,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}がんじがらめの自由なんて僕たちはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:14.66,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}つぎはぎだらけな中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:21.05,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}さよならだけしか見つけられない答えなんてつまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.22,0:01:26.23,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.85,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}探すから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:23.72,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}死体みたいに歩く道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:29.23,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}ギラギラと太陽が照りつける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.44,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}おまえは何時か名前さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.85,0:22:40.15,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}分からなくなるくらい堕ちてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.36,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}人は　何故生きるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:48.03,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}生命　切り刻んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.94,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}終わりなき煩悩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:56.65,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}抱いて踊れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.64,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:09.06,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}渇きの谷から攀じ登れ　風の音が木霊して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:14.79,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}ご覧　我らを導く快楽は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:19.91,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}悲しみを突っ切っていく原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.59,0:23:24.52,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}恐れるな　震えるな　生きるのだ